[An additional 8 Jul 2022 UK Government report indicated that a vaccination program is beginning, and sexual health services will offer the vaccine to anyone considered to be at higher risk of exposure. This includes people with a recent history of multiple partners, participating in group sex, attending sex on premises venues, or have recently had a bacterial sexually transmitted infection (https://www.gov.uk/government/news/monkeypox-continuing-transmission-in-interconnected-sexual-networks). - Mod.TY]
